Uses of Package
io.analytics.domain

  • Packages that use io.analytics.domain 
    Package Description
    io.analytics.domain
    Contains domain objects used for representing data obtained via external data sources such as the Google Analytics API or the application database.
    io.analytics.repository
    Contains classes used for extracting various groups of data from external data sources.
    io.analytics.repository.interfaces  
    io.analytics.service
    Contains classes that Models and Controllers can use to obtain data needed.
    io.analytics.service.interfaces  
    io.analytics.site.models
    Contains model objects used to represent parts in the front end of the application, like particular widgets or sections of the application.
